136
00:13:30,990 --> 00:13:33,823
I'm flattered
that you would like—
No. No.

137
00:13:33,893 --> 00:13:37,829
Justin, please don't
say that sentence.
Sorry. Sorry. I'm sorry.

138
00:13:37,897 --> 00:13:40,195
I'm sorry. I'm sorry.
That's really—

139
00:13:40,266 --> 00:13:42,791
