144
00:13:58,885 --> 00:14:01,046
Then l—

145
00:15:08,387 --> 00:15:11,379
Oh.
A gift.

146
00:15:11,457 --> 00:15:13,925
Oh, thank you.

147
00:15:13,993 --> 00:15:16,587
Thank you.

148
00:15:17,897 --> 00:15:21,094
Thank you so much.
