- Arnold.

150
00:15:26,539 --> 00:15:29,303
That's so nice.

151
00:15:29,375 --> 00:15:31,639
- Isn't it beautiful?
- Yeah.

152
00:15:31,711 --> 00:15:34,441
They made it for me.

153
00:16:12,718 --> 00:16:15,380
Hey, Mr. Bluhm.!

154
00:16:16,756 --> 00:16:18,951
Careful.

155
00:16:19,959 --> 00:16:22,757
Ooh. Take my hand.

156
00:16:26,799 --> 00:16:29,495
