209
00:20:22,635 --> 00:20:26,435
Well, I have. I was there the other night
meeting someone with Arnold.

210
00:20:28,607 --> 00:20:31,007
Oh, well, just a thought.

211
00:20:35,180 --> 00:20:37,444
Sweetheart.

212
00:20:40,119 --> 00:20:43,953
