I'd be ruined.

507
00:39:52,870 --> 00:39:55,134
No one's gonna know, Sandy.

508
00:40:11,489 --> 00:40:13,753
Put it back in the drawer.

509
00:40:13,825 --> 00:40:16,316
Lock the drawer.
Put the key back.

510
00:40:18,062 --> 00:40:20,997
Read it at once.

511
00:40:21,065 --> 00:40:23,397
Promise?
